About Talendy

Connecting world-class engineering talent with innovative companies

Our Story

Talendy was founded in 2022 with a simple mission: to connect the vast pool of engineering talent in India with innovative companies across Asia.

Our founder, Rajiv Mehta, experienced firsthand the challenges of building global tech teams while working as a CTO in Singapore. He recognized that while India produces exceptional engineering talent, connecting these engineers with opportunities abroad remained unnecessarily complex.

What started as a small talent matching service has grown into a comprehensive platform that handles everything from talent discovery to legal compliance, making it seamless for businesses to build distributed engineering teams.

Today, Talendy helps over 150 companies access Indian engineering talent, with a focus on quality, cultural fit, and long-term partnerships.

Our Mission

To create a world where geography is no barrier to accessing opportunity or talent.

Our Vision

To be the premier bridge connecting Indian engineering talent with global innovation.

Our Values

  • Quality over quantity
  • Transparency in all operations
  • Long-term partnership focus
  • Continuous growth and learning
